Nexscholar codebase: Laravel 11 backend with 80+ controllers, services encapsulating AI, content, and taxonomy logic, jobs for embeddings, Google Scholar scraping; Sanctum auth, Bouncer roles, Reverb + Pusher events. Frontend: React 18 + Inertia.js with Tailwind, Shadcn UI, Framer Motion, organized under `resources/js` (Layouts, Hooks, Utils, Components, Pages). Extensive migrations/seeders, queue-based AI pipeline, messaging modules, ScholarLab project management. Cypress E2E and Pest tests.
